previous works, which prepared the precursor firstly followed by heat treatment to obtain the
oxide. However in this work, we report a simple and facile route to achieve (Co,Mn)
hybrid without any following heat treatment. To the best of our knowledge, this is the first time
with outstanding performances. The excellent performance is attributed to synthetic effect of
